OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud and sunny spells
OL,6,Fexpected for much of the day, the best
OL,7,Fof the sunshine perhaps developing in
OL,8,Fthe afternoon from the east, as cloud
OL,9,Fpushes west across the region. Breezy
OL,10,Fat times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly clear overnight,
OL,13,Falthough some isolated fog patches may
OL,14,Fdevelop further inland later in the
OL,15,Fnight. Breezy at times, especially
OL,16,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
