OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAny early morning fog
OL,6,Fpatches will clear quickly to give a
OL,7,Ffine day with plenty of sunny spells.
OL,8,FFeeling breezy at times, especially
OL,9,Ftowards the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FMainly fine in this period, however
OL,13,Flow cloud and patchy fog likely to
OL,14,Fdevelop overnight, with cloudy
OL,15,Fclearing to sunny spells after chilly
OL,16,Fstarts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
